Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory), which deals with the fundamental limits of communication systems. 

The paper also involves analyzing the system performance and proposing a tracking algorithm, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
